      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Prioritizing Veterans' Survivors Act&nbsp;</strong></p><p>This bill provides that the Office of Survivors Assistance (OSA) must operate within the Office of the Secretary of the Department of Veterans Affairs. (Currently, OSA operates within the Pension and Fiduciary Service of the Veterans Benefits Administration.)</p>",
